    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Spring-Framework-개발환경-설정"><a href="#Spring-Framework-개발환경-설정" class="headerlink" title="Spring Framework 개발환경 설정"></a>Spring Framework 개발환경 설정</h1><p><img src="/images/SToshJava_Spring_Logo.png" alt=""></p>
<h2 id="실습환경"><a href="#실습환경" class="headerlink" title="실습환경"></a>실습환경</h2><ul>
<li>OS: Ubuntu 16.04.2 LTS</li>
<li>JDK: 1.8.0_121</li>
<li>IDE: Eclipse_Neon.3 Release (4.6.3)</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="Spring-IDE-설치"><a href="#Spring-IDE-설치" class="headerlink" title="Spring IDE 설치"></a>Spring IDE 설치</h2><p>1) Eclipse [Menu] -&gt; [Help] -&gt; [Install New Software]</p>
<p>2) [Work with]란에<code>http://dist.springsource.com/release/TOOLS/update/e4.6/</code> 입력</p>
<p>3) 설치할 software를 선택 후 [Next]</p>
<p>4) License 내용 [accept] 선택 후 [Finish]</p>
<p><img src="/images/spring_install.gif" alt=""></p>
<hr>
<h2 id="STS-Plugin-설치"><a href="#STS-Plugin-설치" class="headerlink" title="STS Plugin 설치"></a>STS Plugin 설치</h2><p>1) Eclipse [Menu] -&gt; [Marketplace]</p>
<p>2) STS 검색 후 Install</p>
<p><img src="/images/spring_marketplace.png" alt=""></p>
<p>또는, <a href="https://marketplace.eclipse.org/content/spring-tool-suite-sts-eclipse" target="_blank" rel="external">공식 웹사이트 marketplace</a>에서 install tab을 Eclipse로 Drag 하여 설치</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="Spring-Tool-Suite-IDE-설치"><a href="#Spring-Tool-Suite-IDE-설치" class="headerlink" title="Spring Tool Suite IDE 설치"></a>Spring Tool Suite IDE 설치</h2><p><img src="/images/sts.png" alt=""></p>
<p><a href="https://spring.io/tools" target="_blank" rel="external">STS 공식 다운로드 웹페이지</a></p>
